00:32:19.908 --> 00:32:23.408
mutations all the time. So if one of these spontaneous mutations is

559
00:32:23.448 --> 00:32:27.408
promoted in response to TPA or anything else, then you can

560
00:32:27.428 --> 00:32:30.928
get a red tumor. You could also have alternative promoters.

