00:32:32.088 --> 00:32:35.788
I mentioned PFAS, but wounding, and there's a whole range of other promoters that

562
00:32:35.828 --> 00:32:36.588
you could think of.

563
00:32:37.868 --> 00:32:41.528
And then you can maybe stimulate the green cells to give you a green

564
00:32:41.588 --> 00:32:45.548
tumor. So we have this variability in the sources of

565
00:32:45.588 --> 00:32:49.468
the mutant cells and how they respond to their environment, and that's the

566
00:32:49.508 --> 00:32:50.408
end result that we're

567
00:32:51.268 --> 00:32:51.968
trying to measure.

568
00:32:52.888 --> 00:32:56.328
So this is using this TwinStrand approach to try to

569
00:32:56.528 --> 00:33:00.168
track some of these events. The top panel here, each

