00:33:23.728 --> 00:33:27.368
This one has a K-RAS G12D mutation.

577
00:33:28.828 --> 00:33:32.308
There are some H-RAS mutations, some N-RAS mutations.

578
00:33:32.828 --> 00:33:35.828
So these are spontaneous. I'll come back to that in a second.

