00:34:29.129 --> 00:34:29.728
mutations.

595
00:34:31.308 --> 00:34:34.609
We also see spontaneous mutations, as I mentioned,

596
00:34:35.468 --> 00:34:39.328
and this is what happens if you treat the mice only with the promoter,

597
00:34:39.428 --> 00:34:43.288
not with a mutagen. So there are no mutagenic events, exogenous mutagenic

