01:14:11.360 --> 01:14:15.290
trillion cells. But instead of multiplying by all the cells,

1279
01:14:15.360 --> 01:14:19.260
that you can very easily see that many mutations are not going to have any

1280
01:14:20.280 --> 01:14:23.660
importance if the cell is going to die next day and not give progeny.

1281
01:14:24.040 --> 01:14:27.920
So the important cells at risk are the stem cells that

