1286
01:14:41.480 --> 01:14:45.400
And then we can use this probability of a cell of

1287
01:14:45.420 --> 01:14:47.760
a specific mutation to occur in a cell,

1288
01:14:48.760 --> 01:14:50.980
multiply it by the number of cells in that tissue.

